                .columns.is-variable.is-6-desktop
                    .column.is-3
                        %p.eyebrow Competitive Audit
                        %h3 Understanding the market
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1-desktop
                        %p Direct and indirect competitors in the holistic and natural pet food space were analyzed across product presentation, ingredient transparency, educational content, and shopping experience.
                        %p The audit shows that across direct and indirect competitors alike, strong ingredient transparency, smooth product discovery, and educational content have become table stakes in the holistic pet food space. The opportunity for Dr. Harvey's is to close the design and UX gap before the brand's authentic story gets buried by competitors with bigger budgets and cleaner sites.
