            .anchor#brainstorming
            .container
                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %p.eyebrow Brainstorming
                        %h3 Organizing Ideas and the solution
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1
                        %p
                            Considering the research and the goals and frustrations of the personas, the insights were categorized into four areas to aid in generating ideas.
                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %h4 Opportunities
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Clean, human-grade ingredients as a core differentiator
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p 40-year family-owned story with genuine brand heritage
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p No major competitor with both premium quality and authentic warmth
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Vet-endorsed products that can be foregrounded as trust signals
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Growing Gen Z first-time pet owner audience
                        .brainstorming-card.opportunities
                            %p Autoship and loyalty program as untapped retention tools
                    .column.is-3
                        %h4 Pain Points
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Preparation instructions missing or buried on product pages
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Ingredients hard to find and vaguely described
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p No beginner-friendly entry point for first-time owners
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p No recommendation tool for pairing products together
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Trust signals not visible above the fold
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p No blog for easy discovery of the brand
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p Slow loading times
                        .brainstorming-card.pain-points
                            %p No filters by age or needs
                    .column.is-3
                        %h4 Considerations
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Visual identity must feel warm and handcrafted, not clinical
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Copywriting and visual assets handled by client team
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Product range is wide and complex, filtering is critical
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Premium price point requires premium digital quality
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Avoid aggressive sales tactics, authenticity over conversion pressure
                        .brainstorming-card.considerations
                            %p Ingredient-level and condition-specific SEO ensures Dr. Harvey's appears during the research phase
                    .column.is-3
                        %h4 Solutions
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Ingredient lists and preparation guides prominent on every product page
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Pet profile quiz as the primary entry point for new buyers
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Plain-language beginner guide for first-time dehydrated food buyers
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Founder story and brand heritage on homepage and about page
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Autoship and subscription option on all product pages
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Vet endorsements and certifications visible above the fold
                        .brainstorming-card.solutions
                            %p Suggestions of good product pairings on product pages 
        .case-study__features
            .anchor#features
            .container
                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %p.eyebrow Feature Roadmap
                        %h3 Transforming Needs into Features
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1
                        %p
                            Informed by user needs, pain points, and project goals, this feature set prioritizes experiences that reduce friction, build trust, and make holistic pet food easier to understand and shop for.
                .features__features-table
                    %table
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th Page / Feature
                                %th Priority
                                %th Description
                                %th Goal
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td Homepage
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Welcoming homepage communicating brand mission and real-food philosophy. Highlights featured products, displays trust signals, shows the pet profile quiz for easy access, and includes customer reviews above the fold.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                                    %br
                                    %span.sales Sales
                            %tr
                                %td Navigation
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Intuitive navigation browsable by pet type, size or age, and dietary needs. Clear path to the pet quiz from the nav. No more than two levels deep.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.nav Easy Navigation
                                    %br
                                    %span.sales Sales
                            %tr
                                %td Pet profile quiz
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td An interactive quiz matching a dog's age, size, and dietary needs with the most suitable food options. The primary entry point for first-time and overwhelmed buyers.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.nav Easy Navigation
                                    %br
                                    %span.sales Sales
                            %tr
                                %td Product collection
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Product collection page with robust filters by pet type, life stage, dietary need, and format. Quick-shop functionality and all flavor options visible within each product card.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.nav Easy Navigation
                                    %br
                                    %span.sales Sales
                            %tr
                                %td Product detail page
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td Ingredients listed prominently at the top. Preparation and feeding guide immediately below. Benefits, certifications, and vet guidance visible before reviews. Autoship option alongside one-time purchase.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                                    %br
                                    %span.sales Sales
                                    %br
                                    %span.education Education
                            %tr
                                %td Brand story page
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p1 P1 — Must Have
                                %td A page communicating the 40-year company history, founding philosophy, ingredient standards, sourcing commitment, and family-owned values.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                            %tr
                                %td Beginner's guide
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p2 P2 — Good to Have
                                %td A plain-language guide explaining what dehydrated food is, how to prepare it, how to transition from kibble, and what to expect in the first weeks. Directly addresses the biggest barrier for first-time buyers.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.education Education
                                    %br
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                            %tr
                                %td Autoship and subscriptions
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p2 P2 — Good to Have
                                %td Subscription and autoship options on all product pages with clear savings callout. Directly addresses the biggest friction point for repeat buyers.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.retention Retention
                                    %br
                                    %span.sales Sales
                            %tr
                                %td Personalized product pairings
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p2 P2 — Good to Have
                                %td Based on a product a customer is viewing or has purchased before, the site surfaces complementary products like supplements, toppers, or treats that work well together. Reduces decision fatigue for returning buyers and drives discovery of the wider product range.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.retention Retention
                                    %br
                                    %span.sales Sales
                            %tr
                                %td Feeding guides and blog
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p2 P2 — Good to Have
                                %td Educational content on holistic nutrition, feeding guidance, preparation instructions, and ingredient benefits. Positions Dr. Harvey's as an authority in the space.
                                %td.goal
                                    %span.education Education
                                    %br
                                    %span.trust Build Trust
                            %tr
                                %td Ingredient explorer
                                %td.phase
                                    %span.p3 P3 — Nice to Have
